---
import { Icons } from "@components/iconify/icons";
import Iconify from "@components/iconify/iconify.astro";
import CardIcon from "@components/card/card-icon.astro";
import StackIcon from "@components/card/stack-icon.astro";
---

<div
  id="cursos"
  class="h-svh md:h-screen snap-start w-full px-5 py-20 md:px-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-evenly gap-0 lg:gap-8 overflow-hidden"
>
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-5">
    <h2
      class="bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary to-primary bg-clip-text text-transparent font-bold text-5xl md:text-6xl text-center"
    >
      Nuestros Cursos
    </h2>
    <p class="max-w-2xl text-center text-accent/85">
      Potencia tus habilidades y aprende lo esencial del desarrollo web paso a
      paso.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-9 w-full max-w-6xl">
    <div class="flex flex-col-reverse lg:flex-row gap-10">
      <ul class="timeline timeline-vertical flex-1 [&>li>div]:min-w-28">
        <li class="group cursor-pointer">
          <div class="timeline-start font-bold">Commit Master & Dock It</div>
          <div class="timeline-middle">
            <StackIcon icons={[Icons.GIT, Icons.DOCKER]} size={40} />
          </div>
          <div
            class="timeline-end text-xs px-2 group overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 text-center"
          >
            9 - 11 de Septiembre
            <br />
            <p
              class="max-h-0 opacity-0 text-left text-accent/60 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:max-h-20 group-hover:opacity-100"
            >
              Aprende a versionar y dockerizar tus proyectos.
            </p>
          </div>
          <hr class="min-h-[12px] md:min-h-[20px] bg-info" />
        </li>

        <li class="group cursor-pointer">
          <hr class="min-h-[12px] md:min-h-[20px] bg-info" />
          <div class="timeline-start font-bold">Web Starter</div>
          <div class="timeline-middle">
            <StackIcon
              icons={[Icons.HTML, Icons.CSS, Icons.JAVASCRIPT]}
              size={40}
            />
          </div>
          <div
            class="timeline-end text-xs px-2 group overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 text-center"
          >
            Proximamente
            <br />
            <p
              class="max-h-0 opacity-0 text-left text-accent/60 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:max-h-20 group-hover:opacity-100"
            >
              Construye sitios web interactivos desde cero.
            </p>
          </div>
          <hr class="min-h-[12px] md:min-h-[20px] bg-info" />
        </li>

        <li class="group cursor-pointer">
          <hr class="min-h-[12px] md:min-h-[20px] bg-info" />
          <div class="timeline-start font-bold">FigMagic</div>
          <div class="timeline-middle">
            <CardIcon icon={Icons.FIGMA} />
          </div>
          <div
            class="timeline-end text-xs px-2 group overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 text-center"
          >
            Proximamente
            <br />
            <p
              class="max-h-0 opacity-0 text-left text-accent/60 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:max-h-20 group-hover:opacity-100"
            >
              Diseña interfaces y prototipos.
            </p>
          </div>
          <hr class="min-h-[12px] md:min-h-[20px] bg-info" />
        </li>

        <li class="group cursor-pointer">
          <hr
            class="min-h-[12px] md:min-h-[20px] bg-gradient-to-b from-info to-success"
          />
          <div class="timeline-start font-bold">Frontend Turbo</div>
          <div class="timeline-middle">
            <StackIcon icons={[Icons.ASTRO_WEB, Icons.TAILWIND]} size={40} />
          </div>
          <div
            class="timeline-end text-xs px-2 group overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 text-center"
          >
            Proximamente
            <br />
            <p
              class="max-h-0 opacity-0 text-left text-accent/60 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:max-h-20 group-hover:opacity-100"
            >
              Crea sitios web modernos, rápidos y estilizados con Astro y
              Tailwind.
            </p>
          </div>
          <hr class="min-h-[12px] md:min-h-[20px] bg-success" />
        </li>

        <li class="group cursor-pointer">
          <hr class="min-h-[12px] md:min-h-[20px] bg-success" />
          <div class="timeline-start font-bold">Component Pro</div>
          <div class="timeline-middle">
            <StackIcon icons={[Icons.TYPESCRIPT, Icons.REACT]} size={40} />
          </div>
          <div
            class="timeline-end text-xs px-2 group overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 text-center"
          >
            Proximamente
            <br />
            <p
              class="max-h-0 opacity-0 text-left text-accent/60 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:max-h-20 group-hover:opacity-100"
            >
              Desarrolla componentes interactivos.
            </p>
          </div>
          <hr class="min-h-[12px] md:min-h-[20px] bg-success" />
        </li>

        <li class="group cursor-pointer">
          <hr class="min-h-[12px] md:min-h-[20px] bg-success" />
          <div class="timeline-start font-bold">Backend Boost</div>
          <div class="timeline-middle">
            <StackIcon
              icons={[Icons.NESTJS, Icons.FAST_API, Icons.SUPABASE]}
              size={40}
            />
          </div>
          <div
            class="timeline-end text-xs px-2 group overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 text-center"
          >
            Proximamente
            <br />
            <p
              class="max-h-0 opacity-0 text-left text-accent/60 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:max-h-20 group-hover:opacity-100"
            >
              Construye APIs y backends escalables.
            </p>
          </div>
          <hr class="min-h-[12px] md:min-h-[20px] bg-success" />
        </li>

        <li class="group cursor-pointer">
          <hr
            class="min-h-[12px] md:min-h-[20px] bg-gradient-to-b from-secondary to-primary"
          />
          <div class="timeline-start font-bold">DevUps</div>
          <div class="timeline-middle">
            <StackIcon
              icons={[Icons.GITHUB_ACTIONS, Icons.TERRAFORM, Icons.KUBERNETES]}
              size={40}
            />
          </div>
          <div
            class="timeline-end text-xs px-2 overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 text-center"
          >
            Proximamente
            <br />
            <p
              class="max-h-0 opacity-0 text-left text-accent/60 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:max-h-20 group-hover:opacity-100"
            >
              Automatiza, y deploya tus proyectos en la nube.
            </p>
          </div>
          <hr class="min-h-[12px] md:min-h-[20px] bg-primary" />
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class="hidden lg:flex flex-col items-end gap-5 py-0 md:py-10 flex-1">
        <p class="text-justify text-accent/90">
          Como grupo de estudio, hemos preparado un roadmap que te guiará en tu
          aprendizaje de desarrollo web. Si ya tienes conocimientos previos, no
          te preocupes: puedes unirte en la etapa que más te interese.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-4 flex-1">
          <div class="card text-info bg-info/30 w-full shadow-sm">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h4 class="card-title"><Iconify icon={Icons.BASIC} />Básico</h4>
              <p>
                Aprenderás los fundamentos de HTML, CSS y conceptos básicos de
                JavaScript. Esta etapa es ideal para quienes se inician en el
                desarrollo web.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card text-success bg-success/30 w-full shadow-sm">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h4 class="card-title">
                <Iconify icon={Icons.INTERMEDIATE} />Intermedio
              </h4>
              <p>
                Profundizarás en JavaScript, frameworks como React y buenas
                prácticas de desarrollo. Aquí aprenderás a crear aplicaciones
                más complejas y dinámicas.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div
            class="card text-neutral bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary w-full shadow-sm after:bg-gradient-to-br after:from-primary after:to-secondary after:absolute after:top-1.5 after:right-2 after:left-2 after:bottom-2 after:card after:blur-lg after:scale-105 after:-z-10 after:transition-all after:duration-300 after:opacity-80"
          >
            <div class="card-body bg-base-200 text-accent m-1.5 rounded-xl">
              <h4 class="card-title">
                <Iconify icon={Icons.ADVANCED} />Avanzado
              </h4>
              <p>
                Te enfocarás en optimización, testing, arquitectura y despliegue
                de aplicaciones web. Esta etapa prepara para proyectos
                profesionales y trabajo en equipo.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
